title: NASA's Artemis 2 moon rocket has a new problem. 'This will almost assuredly impact the March launch window.'
description: NASA is troubleshooting a glitch with the upper stage of Artemis 2's Space Launch System rocket that will likely delay the launch of the moon mission.
content: NASA is troubleshooting a glitch with the upper stage of Artemis 2's Space Launch System rocket that will likely delay the launch of the moon mission.
